    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252330/extras/a728970cc7945f96e16114945b54e063.poster.avif?t=1721126313\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252330/extras/a728970cc7945f96e16114945b54e063.webm?t=1721126313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252330/extras/a728970cc7945f96e16114945b54e063.mp4?t=1721126313\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在这个激动人心的闲置点击游戏中，加入点击守护者的行列。与战士、法师和盗贼一起，你将开始一次史诗般的旅程，拯救这个领域免受古老邪恶的威胁。你将使用各种武器和能力与大量怪物和强大的首领战斗。一切都从一个点击开始！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252330/extras/5fffce4d0511e205e33fbf9c08d4c50e.webp?t=1721126313\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252330/extras/5fffce4d0511e205e33fbf9c08d4c50e.poster.avif?t=1721126313\" class=\"bb_img\" width=50 height=50 /></picture></span><strong>玩起来像点击游戏，但感觉像RPG游戏</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252330/extras/6bfe41f5b8d75a5392536e3efe40d946.webp?t=1721126313\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252330/extras/6bfe41f5b8d75a5392536e3efe40d946.poster.avif?t=1721126313\" class=\"bb_img\" width=50 height=50 /></picture></span></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252330/extras/3a9560973c2345c460b962fade7219df.poster.avif?t=1721126313\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252330/extras/3a9560973c2345c460b962fade7219df.webm?t=1721126313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252330/extras/3a9560973c2345c460b962fade7219df.mp4?t=1721126313\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>累积大量金币、资源和经验并重新投资你的角色和同伴们。利用自由的制作系统获得最稀有的物品。<br>你下一步的升级将会有五花八门的选择。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252330/extras/5fffce4d0511e205e33fbf9c08d4c50e.webp?t=1721126313\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252330/extras/5fffce4d0511e205e33fbf9c08d4c50e.poster.avif?t=1721126313\" class=\"bb_img\" width=50 height=50 /></picture></span><strong>你不寻常的常见敌人</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252330/extras/6bfe41f5b8d75a5392536e3efe40d946.webp?t=1721126313\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252330/extras/6bfe41f5b8d75a5392536e3efe40d946.poster.avif?t=1721126313\" class=\"bb_img\" width=50 height=50 /></picture></span></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252330/extras/7b3d93035f914a919c9be5ce820cd77d.poster.avif?t=1721126313\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252330/extras/7b3d93035f914a919c9be5ce820cd77d.webm?t=1721126313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252330/extras/7b3d93035f914a919c9be5ce820cd77d.mp4?t=1721126313\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>面对许多有趣的幻想怪物，都以独特的体素外观重新塑造。通过自己的战斗将他们化为灰烬，或者放轻松来让你的守护者同伴来完成任务。<br>点击守护者同样支持主动和被动的游戏风格。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252330/extras/5fffce4d0511e205e33fbf9c08d4c50e.webp?t=1721126313\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252330/extras/5fffce4d0511e205e33fbf9c08d4c50e.poster.avif?t=1721126313\" class=\"bb_img\" width=50 height=50 /></picture></span><strong>足够的内容可以点击一辈子</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252330/extras/6bfe41f5b8d75a5392536e3efe40d946.webp?t=1721126313\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252330/extras/6bfe41f5b8d75a5392536e3efe40d946.poster.avif?t=1721126313\" class=\"bb_img\" width=50 height=50 /></picture></span></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252330/extras/8382b8476aba06076f6aea87241a2405.poster.avif?t=1721126313\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252330/extras/8382b8476aba06076f6aea87241a2405.webm?t=1721126313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252330/extras/8382b8476aba06076f6aea87241a2405.mp4?t=1721126313\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>通过大量阶段进展，并提升你公会中的阶级，与越来越强大的首领作战。<br>守护人从不睡觉，因为拐角处总是有新的任务！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252330/extras/09e7e743d495ff153dfa2bd0c8e56dea.poster.avif?t=1721126313\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252330/extras/09e7e743d495ff153dfa2bd0c8e56dea.webm?t=1721126313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252330/extras/09e7e743d495ff153dfa2bd0c8e56dea.mp4?t=1721126313\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h